Package: dde-folder-preview-plugin
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Folder preview plugin for DDE File Manager
 A DDE File Manager preview plugin that displays a rich visual summary
 of directory contents when the user presses Space on a folder.
 .
 Features include a header panel with folder icon and path, stat badges
 showing file count, sub-folder count and total recursive size (via du),
 and a sortable file list with name, type, size and last-modified columns.
